1) from superAdmin create 2 users with USER role
2) try to login with non exist user
3) promote 1 user to Admin
4) try to create article from User role (but only admins can create)
Steps 5-7 should be done by user with "Admin" role.
5) Create 3 different articles
6) show 1 of them
7) update one article
Steps 8-10 should be done by user with "User" role.
8) list all articles for a given author
9) list all articles for a given period
10) find all articles for a specific keyword
11) delete all articles by user with "Admin" role.